<li><strong>Gemini 2.5 Pro</strong>: $1.25/M input, $5/M output</li>

</ul>

<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4">Together's Llama 4 Maverick at $0.27/$0.85 is <strong>roughly 13x cheaper on input</strong> and <strong>16x cheaper on output</strong> than GPT-5.6, while sitting within 3-5 percentage points on most reasoning benchmarks.</p>

